@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/admin
@accessToken = REPLACE_ME

### Top selling products (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/analytics/top-selling
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Top selling products (custom)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/analytics/top-selling?days=30&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Top favorited products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/analytics/top-favorited?days=30&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Least bought products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/analytics/least-bought?days=30&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
